      "content": "it's not just mistakes though. it's constant. i look at how much they struggle because of my choices and i realized that my presence is actually the problem. they act like they're okay but i can see it in their eyes. they're just constantly dealing with my chaos. i keep thinking that if i wasn't even around, they could finally just breathe and start over without me holding them back.",
