    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"professional guidance\" feels so empty. it doesn't change the fact that i'm the common denominator in all their problems. if i just disappeared, the chaos would actually stop. they could have a clean slate. it almost feels more selfish to keep staying and causing them more pain than to just make a choice that lets them move on.",
